{"tid":894586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手遊引爆負評，暗黑團隊出面：我們都聽到了，內部討論未間斷","createTime":"2018-11-08T13:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T06:05:26.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fb214b16779ea6acea04952fe59aacd96cc175","tid":894586,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"針對近日連續不斷的負評風浪，《暗黑破壞神》的社群經理 Nevalistis 今（8）日稍早出面說明：「讓我以這句話開頭：我們都聽到你們的心聲了。」<br />\n <br />\nNevalistis 表示，在 BlizzCon 2018 結束，週一進公司後，暗黑團隊就馬不停蹄的在討論相關事務，他們會持續傾聽玩家的心聲並與之互動，也希望玩家能夠不斷給予他們有建樹的意見，社群團隊會把這些意見轉給內部開發人員討論，並且會第一時間把可公布的消息讓玩家知道。<br />\n <br />\n雖然我們近期可能還是不會聽到 D4 的相關消息，但根據 Nevalistis 在 BlizzCon 中與實況主的討論，D3 新賽季會有一些新東西等著玩家，而她目前也已正在著手寫相關的部落格文章。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hdkk0Ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdkk0Ff.png&h=6d436d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8dR7kg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8dR7kg.png&h=032ba2d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbfad8a537b01bc834f58fdc2f1abfd18deed16b","tid":894586,"uid":14715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"等6年結果出呢隻淨係用來搵錢既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd職業畫風都同第3代一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係fans我都嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90ace80174105f645bdd894db3e06233081b17e","tid":894586,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"2代多人玩都唔用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f60fa46cee28ba0303d6e8679c88b473d348a0","tid":894586,"uid":152512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"貨金俾暴雪我不如支持下Rockstar 同埋CD project 好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f623282351aea05cd05899b31942650ca1dfa248","tid":894586,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"等睇班fans屌住黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521b6225760b182b69bc517a83f745f8082feca3","tid":894586,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f623282351aea05cd05899b31942650ca1dfa248","tid":894586,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"等睇班fans屌住黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"繼續玩d2/3 都唔會玩呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩得pc diablo 既多數都係hardcore gamer， 唔會睇得mobile game上眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我雖然唔算fans，但隻d3出果時都有排隊買，買返來淨玩hardcore， 玩到個垃圾拍賣場通漲到咁上下就無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171ab0ef4dcab908be6f3516a67e5991ea880d4b","tid":894586,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4V1L9T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4V1L9T.gif&h=51306f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DpmMaA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DpmMaA.gif&h=90ef0b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估下邊隻係d3，邊隻係immortal <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2bf5ea4149a80d9cfc55fd27695bfadb50b6fb","tid":894586,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"171ab0ef4dcab908be6f3516a67e5991ea880d4b","tid":894586,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4V1L9T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4V1